          MODULE=vim-exvim
         VERSION=0.5.0
          SOURCE=$MODULE-$VERSION.tar.gz
SOURCE_DIRECTORY=$BUILD_DIRECTORY/main-$VERSION
SOURCE_URL_FULL=https://github.com/exvim/main/archive/v$VERSION.tar.gz
      SOURCE_VFY=sha256:08709236e70cfa2646203c15b46b6cddbf858a866849cc3a52ff860e2efff0f3
        WEB_SITE=http://exvim.github.io/
         ENTERED=20160427
         UPDATED=20160427
           SHORT="Make the vim as an IDE like environment"

cat << EOF
exVim is a project to turn Vim into a nice programming environment.
It introduce the project file concept (.exvim) in Vim. By editing this project
file (.exvim) through Vim, the exVim plugins will be invoked. In this way, it
makes you possible to apply different Vim settings, plugin settings and even
loading plugins on demand by different projects.
EOF
